{"tid":590721,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人真係試過畀人盜用身分證借錢？","createTime":"2018-03-13T01:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T12:12:41.000Z","uid":6097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea19d892182a5b17538d7d802093ee091671419d","tid":590721,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T01:37:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n尋日臨收工急屎<br />\n就放低咗個銀包去爆石<br />\n咁出到黎得返我一個就咋咋臨執嘢走<br />\n<br />\n咁我身分證同易賞錢卡係放喺同一卡位<br />\n去到百佳畀錢先發現 我張易賞錢變咗打橫放<br />\n我一向習慣都係打直放 方便我拎<br />\n<br />\n所以我就諗會唔會有人郁過我銀包<br />\n好驚畀人拎去借錢/申請服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要唔要放工去警署報失先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38d65558f9c75f87825a44713dd1383d75dcecc","tid":590721,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"好賤呀啲財仔<br />\n唔使露面就可以借錢 好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa12971544c6a841509bbcb4beec2f5db6d810e","tid":590721,"uid":304334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"師兄而家有冇事？"},{"pid":"1e6d716fd971a37a13e9438bed78bc30985c8062","tid":590721,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa12971544c6a841509bbcb4beec2f5db6d810e","tid":590721,"uid":304334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"師兄而家有冇事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"哇點解推返舊post嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你畀人盜用咗？"},{"pid":"018cad347fb38ecae9e9e9aa43c1dcf836b4b80a","tid":590721,"uid":304334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"我上連登自爆咗"}]}